T1  - Toward a Theory of Organization Communication: Consideration in Channel Selection
AU  - Melcher, Arlyn J.
AU  - Beller, Ronald
Y1  - 1967/03/01
PY  - 1967
DA  - 1967/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/255243
